							$\hat {\beta }_{i,j}\in [0,1]$
						\end{document}β^i,j∈[0,1] for i={1,…,n} samples and j={1,…,p} CpG sites assayed. We thresholded this output to predict the binary methylation status of each CpG site, \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
